{"id":31094,"date":"2023-06-16T15:39:12","date_gmt":"2023-06-16T19:39:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.concentrix.com\/?p=31094"},"modified":"2023-06-16T17:12:50","modified_gmt":"2023-06-16T21:12:50","slug":"chris-caldwell-named-as-best-ceo-for-women-diversity","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.concentrix.com\/about\/news\/press-release\/chris-caldwell-named-as-best-ceo-for-women-diversity\/","title":{"rendered":"Chris Caldwell Named as Best CEO for Women, Diversity"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-comparably-ranks-concentrix-s-leadership-based-on-global-staff-feedback\">Comparably ranks Concentrix\u2019s Leadership based on global staff feedback<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Location: Newark, CA<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Date: June 14, 2023<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Concentrix is proud to be recognized with three annual Comparably awards in leadership categories. CEO Chris Caldwell has once again been placed on the list for both Best CEOs for Women and Best CEOs for Diversity. Additionally, Concentrix was recognized on the Best Company Leadership list for the second time.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Winning these awards demonstrates that people-first culture starts at the top with leadership commitments to embracing staff differences and creating inclusive and safe workplaces for global staff to thrive in their careers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Comparably awards are determined by anonymous feedback provided by current staff. On Comparably, staff are encouraged to leave their candid opinions on their career experience at Concentrix. We remain proud that global staff think highly of Concentrix and feel compelled to share their positive experiences with the world.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Concentrix is proud to be recognized with three annual Comparably awards in leadership categories. CEO Chris Caldwell has once again been placed on the list for both Best CEOs for Women and Best CEOs for D